node.text:
🛫 SKYDIVING LIVE VIDEO: You can reach everything in life, if you overcome your inner fears ... JUST DO IT !! What can we learn from skydiving? 🛬
⠀
✅ Those who don't jump will never fly.
⠀
✅  Do one thing every day that scares you.
⠀
✅ Skydiving changed my mindset. I am teaching my team and my kids, they could do anything and do it well, if they overcome fears.
⠀
✅ Once you have tasted flying or skydiving, you will never walk the earth with your eyes turned skyward, for there you have been, and there you will always long to return.
⠀
✅ I learned that courage was not the absence of fear, but the triumph over it. The brave man is not he who does not feel afraid, but he who conquers that fear.
⠀
✅ You don't need a parachute to skydive. You only need a parachute to skydive twice 😂🤣 ha ha ha 🤣😂.
⠀
. 
.
⠀

⚠️ Tag your squad! Double tap if you agree! ✅
🔑Success is always more fun when your whole squad wins.🔑

👉🏼 It’s not the team with the best players that win, it’s the players with the best team.
⠀
👉🏼 Teamwork is the ability to work together toward a common vision. The ability to direct individual accomplishments toward organizational objectives. It is the fuel that allows common people to attain uncommon results. ⠀

👉🏼 If there is any one secret of success, it lies in the ability to get the other person’s point of view and see things from that person’s angle as well as from my own. (Henry Ford) ⠀

👉🏼 My model for business is The Beatles. They were four guys who kept each other’s kind of negative tendencies in check. They balanced each other and the total was greater than the sum of its parts. That’s how I see business: great things in business are never done by one person. They’re done by a team of people. (Steve Jobs)

👉🏼 You need to be aware of what others are doing, applaud their efforts, acknowledge their successes and encourage them in their pursuits. When we all help one another, everybody wins.

👉🏼 Alone, we can do so little; together we can do so much.

node.text:
❤️SECRETS of successful LOVE & RELATIONSHIPS ❤️

✅ Fact: We're born alone, we live alone, we die alone. Only through our love and friendship can we create the illusion for the moment that we're not alone.

✅ Every relationship can be successful. But in order for that to happen you'll always need love, trust, respect, and honesty to help you remain in love. Be understanding even when your partner frustrates you. Spend time together, and make sure that you both understand each other.
 
✅ Immature love says: 'I love you because I need you.' Mature love says 'I need you because I love you.'

✅ Love is always bestowed as a gift - freely, willingly and without expectation. We don't love to be loved; we love to love. But love isn't something you find. Love is something that finds you.

✅ Practice mindfulness. Recommit, every day. Be playful. Put work into the relationship. If it's not important, let it go. When there is conflict, talk it out. Show your love. Hold hands. Always trust and try to forgive. Don't forget to hug.

✅ Focus on what the partner is doing right, not what they do wrong; compliment your partner when they deserve it, and try not to look for things they do wrong. "You can always find something".

✅ Say "I love you" and "have a good day" every morning. Saying something caring like that first thing will set the other up for their day. And: Say goodnight, every night. Regardless of how you feel. Never go to bed on an argument

✅ Communication is the best way to create strong and lasting relationships.
⠀

node.text:
🔑If opportunity does not knock, build a door.🔑

👉🏼 Sometimes, it's all about creating that right opportunity instead of just waiting for it to come. You can't always rely on chance. We need to create opportunities that will lead to our goals and success.
⠀
👉🏼 The crux of this quote is ACTION. You can choose how much and how drastic of an action you want to take to get that opportunity, it could be anything from self-improvement to networking, but you still need to take that action to attain the opportunity. ⠀

👉🏼 The opportunities you need to create can depend on developing personality, personal attributes or simply mechanical steps such as filing a resume. ⠀

👉🏼 Without a door, opportunity has nothing to knock on. The specific door you should build depends on what sort of opportunities you are interested in.

👉🏼 Keep taking the RIGHT ACTION, action which excited you the most until you grab that opportunity.
⠀
⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇

🔑You know you're on the right track when you're not interested in looking back.🔑

👉🏼 Continue to be successful after doing something with good results in the past.
⠀
👉🏼 Become increasingly successful by doing things different and BETTER. Move forward and never look back because no matter what had happened, it becomes history. ⠀

👉🏼 Start enjoying your work, then you never look back. This is a clear indication that you are on right track. ⠀

👉🏼 If you only pay attention to your past, how can you think clearly about your future? While it’s important to learn from your mistakes, it’s also important to keep looking ahead.

👉🏼 If you never look back, it doesn’t mean that you don’t remember where you’ve come from. You should think about your progress in life to appreciate how successful you are today. But don’t spend too much time on the “what ifs.”

👉🏼 Learn to let go of the past in order to fucus on the life ahead of you.
⠀
⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇

🔑How do you live a happy life?🔑
⠀
✔️Find your passion and follow it
✔️Stop constantly listening to other people's opinions
✔️Create an action plan for your goals
✔️Surround yourself with people who support you on your way
✔️Always educate yourself
✔️Improve your skills and stand out from the crowd
⠀

🔑 LESSONS OF LIFE 🔑
⠀
✅ Luck is when preparation meets opportunity.
⠀
✅ In the end we only regret the things, the joy and chances we didn't take. So start living.
⠀
✅ No matter what happens in life, be good to people. Being good to people is a wonderful legacy to leave behind.
⠀
✅ The only limit to our realization of tomorrow will be our doubts of today.
⠀
✅ Just celebrate the life you had, not the life you could've had.
⠀
⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇

node.text:
🔑Quality is the best business plan.🔑

👉🏼 Quality means you'll be happy with what you're selling and your customers will be happy with what they get. It also means you'll have word-of-mouth recommendations as your customers will talk about it, and that's a marketing tool that can't be substituted. ⠀

👉🏼 With that in mind, here are some of the qualities of a good business plan, in order of importance: ⠀

✅ It fits the business need.
✅ It's realistic.
✅ It's specific.
✅ It clearly defines responsibilities for implementation.
✅ It clearly identifies assumptions.
✅ It's communicated to the people who have to run it.
✅ It gets people committed.
⠀
⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇⬇
